\[\nabla^{2}_{\bm{q}}S=\begin{bmatrix}\nabla^{2}_{\bm{q}_{1}}S&\nabla^{2}_{\bm{ q}_{2}\bm{q}_{2}}S\\ \nabla^{2}_{\bm{q}_{2}\bm{q}_{1}}S&\nabla^{2}_{\bm{q}_{2}}S\end{bmatrix}\] (42)

